\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2520,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/24\/most-hated-prophet-lies\/","url_meta":{"origin":35265,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dishonesty: Most hated behavior to the Prophet was lying","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: There was no behavior more hateful to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, than dishonesty. A man would tell a lie when speaking in the presence of the Prophet, and he would not be satisfied until he knew that he had repented from it.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24850,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/24\/salaf-fasting-remember-poor\/","url_meta":{"origin":35265,"position":2},"title":"Salaf on Fasting: Remember the poor, starving while fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 24, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Hassan ibn Ahmad reported: He asked the commander of the faithful Al-Ma'mun 'Ali ibn Musa al-Rida, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cIs there any benefit to fasting in the wisdom?\u201d Al-Ma'mun said, \u201cAllah Almighty knows what the impoverished endure of severe hunger, so He made the rich perform fasting\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"